curam.core.impl
Class SearchServiceMapperForStreaming

java.lang.Object
  curam.core.impl.SearchServiceMapper
      curam.core.impl.SearchServiceMapperForStreaming
All Implemented Interfaces:
Mapper, StreamableMapper
public class SearchServiceMapperForStreaming
extends SearchServiceMapper
implements StreamableMapper

Adds batch streaming capability to the generic search mapping class. This consists of a method to convert a key struct to a byte array and vice versa. The byte array gets stored on the batch chunk tables during stream execution.
